These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-1::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, frog, goldfish, rabbit
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, satire, horror, time-travel
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, green, purple
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, nurse, dressmaker, writer
 1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
 3. the owner of the horse is not the nurse##6
 4. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
 5. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes purple##5
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 7. the person who likes chestnut is the owner of the horse##1
 8. the owner of the horse is between the dressmaker and the person watching superhero movies##2
 9. the doctor is on the left of the person who likes green##1
10. the writer is not the person watching satire movies##6
11. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
13. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | goldfish     | horse      | rabbit      | frog    |
| Food          | superhero    | satire | time-travel | horror     |
| Music-Genre   | purple    | chestnut     | green    | blue     |
| Nationality   | writer | doctor | dressmaker    | nurse |

