The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, snowmobile, skateboard
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, pakistani, nigerian, polish
 1. the nigerian is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the polish##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 4. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
 5. the polish is in an even position##4
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person driving the train and the person watching superhero movies##2
 7. the person driving the train is on the right of the nigerian##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
10. the russian is the person who likes brown##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person driving the train is not the nigerian##6
13. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person driving the train##1
14. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food          | martial-arts    | superhero | time-travel | family       |
