 6. the person traveling to colone is not the person eating radish##6
 7. the person eating blueberry is not the person traveling to colone##6
 8. the person who growsbegonia is between the owner of the horse and the person traveling to colone##2
 9. the owner of the bird is the person eating artichoke##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person eating artichoke is in an odd position##4
12. the owner of the bird is the person traveling to colone##1
13. the person eating orange is the person who growsbegonia##1

