 6. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the person eating blueberry is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
10. the person who likes lilac is not the vegafina-smoker##6
11. the person eating avocado is the person eating avocado##1
12. the person eating avocado is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's sport is baseball##2
13. the person who's sport is baseball is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | rowing | baseball     | parkour    | cycling |
| Music-Genre   | banana | lemon       | avocado | blueberry    |
| Pet           | baccarat    | siglo | vegafina      | dannemann |
| Transport     | azure     | lilac     | mauve     | aquamarine |

